{"tid":1303024,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[讀社科悔終生] 對社會科學有興趣或者唔知社科讀啲咩既可以入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:25:32.000Z","uid":199092,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"37c7d61f3e827ad8ffe57e91ee9499c66444a071","tid":1303024,"uid":199092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"見到隔離排jupas post好多人都對社科有興趣<br />\n想開個post介紹番社會科學係讀啲咩<br />\n首先要釐清下<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 讀社科=/=搞社運</span></span></strong> 如果你係因為最近既反送中運動 見到社會既不公義而想讀社科去改變社會 你就諗多咗喇 讀<br />\n社會科學入面有地理學、心理學、政治學、社會學<br />\n講住咁多先 其他同路人可以喺下面講下自己讀緊既社科係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d077b2c130b19807263d6e48cac252ea1697c1","tid":1303024,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f93b442d43713a91ca48d4acccf879985280f7ac","tid":1303024,"uid":66970,"like":12,"dislike":6,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:05:33.000Z","msg":"社會學幾好<br />\n讀完個人諗嘢闊咗<br />\n分析力好咗<br />\n但無對應嘅職業<br />\n不過本人認為搵唔搵到工係睇你叻唔叻，<br />\n而唔係讀咩科出身<br />\n<br />\n利申中大soci grad"},{"pid":"17bdef1e1b919ab8b88fa6997087908772886da9","tid":1303024,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b2dbbe800f382a1453dce08ac2e80804796a21","tid":1303024,"uid":199092,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"想讀JS6717既DSE同學<br />\nHKU sosci入面有個programme叫GCSI 係compulsory要去做intern 唔做畢唔到業<br />\n但係個internship係冇人工 係冇錢收㗎！<br />\n最多faculty會喺你做完之後俾番500蚊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a69b5aa05b175a9f7585ee4cfff063348ed2c7","tid":1303024,"uid":199092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f93b442d43713a9